---

## Finding Files Older Than 3 Days

Use `find` with the `-mtime +3` flag (`+3` means **more than** 3 days since modification):
| Flag | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `-mtime +3` | Modified **more than** 3 days ago |
| `-type f` | Regular files only |
| `-type d` | Directories only |
| `-ls` | Long listing with details |

**Common options:**
- `-atime` — last **access** time
- `-ctime` — last **status change** time
- Add `-delete` to remove matched files (use with caution!)
EOF
